<TITLE>Crisis deepens in Tripura</TITLE>


<TEXT>
Tripura (Central) University authority had to <EVENT eid="e1" class="OCCURRENCE">step</EVENT> back from the <EVENT eid="e2" class="OCCURRENCE">decision</EVENT> to <EVENT eid="e3" class="OCCURRENCE">send</EVENT> Dean (Arts   Commerce) in waiting <EVENT eid="e4" class="OCCURRENCE">anticipating</EVENT> further trouble for Vice Chancellor Prof A K Ghosh who is <EVENT eid="e5" class="I_ACTION">accused</EVENT> of series of <EVENT eid="e6" class="OCCURRENCE">corruption</EVENT> during his <TIMEX3 tid="t1" type="DURATION" value="P4Y">four years</TIMEX3> tenure. A section of university teachers <EVENT eid="e7" class="OCCURRENCE">raised allegation</EVENT> against Dean (Arts   Commerce) Prof Satyadeo Poddar for <EVENT eid="e8" class="OCCURRENCE">approving</EVENT> illegal academic activities of VC in <TIMEX3 tid="t2" type="DATE" value="PAST_REF">past few months</TIMEX3> and also <EVENT eid="e9" class="OCCURRENCE">involved</EVENT> in screening process of candidature of the aspirants to the post of associate professor in four departments. While <EVENT eid="e10" class="OCCURRENCE">demanding</EVENT> removal of VC immediately, the teachers also <EVENT eid="e11" class="OCCURRENCE">asked</EVENT> for suspension of Dean Prof Poddar and <EVENT eid="e12" class="OCCURRENCE">instituting</EVENT> independent <EVENT eid="e13" class="OCCURRENCE">inquiry</EVENT> into the entire volume of purchase and appointments <EVENT eid="e14" class="OCCURRENCE">done</EVENT> during the <EVENT eid="e15" class="OCCURRENCE">tenure</EVENT> of incumbent VC Prof Ghosh. Following pressure from the teachers and to <EVENT eid="e16" class="OCCURRENCE">save</EVENT> his skin, VC <EVENT eid="e17" class="I_ACTION">committed</EVENT> to the agitating teachers that he would <EVENT eid="e18" class="OCCURRENCE">remove</EVENT> Prof Poddar from Deanship. But Prof Poddar <EVENT eid="e19" class="OCCURRENCE">fought</EVENT> back to VC <EVENT eid="e20" class="OCCURRENCE">accusing</EVENT> him of compelling each and every one of the university administration to <EVENT eid="e21" class="OCCURRENCE">regularise</EVENT> his decisions. "Not only in case of recruitment, The VC is the final authority of <EVENT eid="e22" class="OCCURRENCE">taking</EVENT> all the <EVENT eid="e23" class="OCCURRENCE">decisions</EVENT> including academic activities. In several instances, VC <EVENT eid="e24" class="I_ACTION">made</EVENT> us <EVENT eid="e25" class="I_ACTION">comply</EVENT> to <EVENT eid="e26" class="OCCURRENCE">perform</EVENT> in <EVENT eid="e27" class="REPORTING">according</EVENT> to his choice and some cases we <EVENT eid="e28" class="I_STATE">forced</EVENT> him to <EVENT eid="e29" class="OCCURRENCE">change</EVENT> the <EVENT eid="e30" class="OCCURRENCE">decision</EVENT>. In particular case of elevation of an assistant professor to <EVENT eid="e31" class="OCCURRENCE">associate</EVENT> in Rural Development Department, I was on leave and this was <EVENT eid="e32" class="OCCURRENCE">scrutinised</EVENT> by other Deans. How can I be responsible for this, VC must <EVENT eid="e33" class="I_ACTION">clarify</EVENT> before <EVENT eid="e34" class="OCCURRENCE">taking</EVENT> any <EVENT eid="e35" class="OCCURRENCE">action</EVENT> against me," Prof Poddar <EVENT eid="e36" class="REPORTING">told</EVENT> openly in the <EVENT eid="e37" class="OCCURRENCE">meeting</EVENT> of the administrative committee. The university administration had <EVENT eid="e38" class="OCCURRENCE">stepped</EVENT> back from the <EVENT eid="e39" class="OCCURRENCE">decision</EVENT> after Prof Poddar <EVENT eid="e40" class="OCCURRENCE">raised</EVENT> voice. Meantime, a group of teachers stand behind Prof Poddar and ultimately revolt against VC and Register. They however, also <EVENT eid="e41" class="OCCURRENCE">demanded</EVENT> inquiry into the allegations by an independent authority to <EVENT eid="e42" class="OCCURRENCE">unearth</EVENT> the truth and <EVENT eid="e43" class="REPORTING">added</EVENT>, "Academic atmosphere has <EVENT eid="e44" class="OCCURRENCE">gone</EVENT> down drastically in the university because of maladministration and students and scholars did not <EVENT eid="e45" class="OCCURRENCE">get</EVENT> any support for <EVENT eid="e46" class="OCCURRENCE">attending</EVENT> seminar and workshop while VC and his team has been <EVENT eid="e47" class="OCCURRENCE">looting</EVENT> out the public fund." Earlier VC had <EVENT eid="e48" class="OCCURRENCE">recruited</EVENT> librarian, deputy librarian, finance officer and many other important posts of the university adopting unfair means and <EVENT eid="e49" class="OCCURRENCE">accused</EVENT> of a large scale corruption of procuring e-book in the university. The VC <EVENT eid="e50" class="OCCURRENCE">favoured</EVENT> a teacher in <EVENT eid="e51" class="OCCURRENCE">screening</EVENT> for elevation of associate professor who has <EVENT eid="e52" class="OCCURRENCE">engaged</EVENT> his daughter in Rural Development department under a project. The VC is also <EVENT eid="e53" class="OCCURRENCE">accused</EVENT> of <EVENT eid="e54" class="OCCURRENCE">dedicating</EVENT> a <EVENT eid="e55" class="OCCURRENCE">furnish building</EVENT> and <EVENT eid="e56" class="OCCURRENCE">provided</EVENT> funding to one NGO run by his wife, they <EVENT eid="e57" class="REPORTING">alleged</EVENT>. UNI BB KK
</TEXT>


